Shireen Crutchfield https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shireen_Crutchfield 0 Shireen Elaine Crutchfield (born December 29, 1970 in Cambridge, Massachusetts) is an American actress and singer. best known as the lead singer of the R trio The Good Girls from 1989-Present. Crutchfield is also known for her acting roles as Jace on the series Dark Angel and the movie Hot Boyz.
